  "detailed_description": "VR bowling, designed from the ground-up for VR with advanced physics to capture the feeling of real bowling.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1585930/extras/b19eba1b09d778a57f92bfe287ccfdf2.poster.avif?t=1665668465\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1585930/extras/b19eba1b09d778a57f92bfe287ccfdf2.webm?t=1665668465\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1585930/extras/b19eba1b09d778a57f92bfe287ccfdf2.mp4?t=1665668465\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1585930/extras/32fd6ce49f21d6b2cf06c41a37f65957.poster.avif?t=1665668465\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1585930/extras/32fd6ce49f21d6b2cf06c41a37f65957.webm?t=1665668465\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1585930/extras/32fd6ce49f21d6b2cf06c41a37f65957.mp4?t=1665668465\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Detailed lane oil simulation and configuration allow you set-up the game you want to play.<br></li><li> Advanced tracking options to work well with both inside-out tracking and base-stations.<br></li><li> Assists for beginners.<br></li><li> A range of AI opponents to bowl against.<br></li><li> Local hotseat games to play with friends.<br></li><li> Bowl-Lab and detailed statistics to help you improve your play.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "VR bowling, designed from the ground-up for VR with advanced physics to capture the feeling of real bowling.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1585930/extras/b19eba1b09d778a57f92bfe287ccfdf2.poster.avif?t=1665668465\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1585930/extras/b19eba1b09d778a57f92bfe287ccfdf2.webm?t=1665668465\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1585930/extras/b19eba1b09d778a57f92bfe287ccfdf2.mp4?t=1665668465\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1585930/extras/32fd6ce49f21d6b2cf06c41a37f65957.poster.avif?t=1665668465\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1585930/extras/32fd6ce49f21d6b2cf06c41a37f65957.webm?t=1665668465\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1585930/extras/32fd6ce49f21d6b2cf06c41a37f65957.mp4?t=1665668465\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Detailed lane oil simulation and configuration allow you set-up the game you want to play.<br></li><li> Advanced tracking options to work well with both inside-out tracking and base-stations.<br></li><li> Assists for beginners.<br></li><li> A range of AI opponents to bowl against.<br></li><li> Local hotseat games to play with friends.<br></li><li> Bowl-Lab and detailed statistics to help you improve your play.</li></ul>",
